ygData.messageBody:
i have not purchased level 29 psalm of vitality or level 37 psalm of purity because the only info i have seen on them is that they increase SV for disease and poison. i never found these very useful, and also found it strange that two songs, both high level, would have this effect. does anyone have any actual experience using them?

also, level 35 denon's dissension, i have bought and used, though i don't really know what effect it is having on the targets. i guess it could just be an exact upgrade of level 18 denon's disruptive discord, but if anyone knows it's true effects i'd love to know if it does anything different.

Shada D'ukal, level 37 wood elf bard, Mithaniel Marr

Mike
